text: Allaysky () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Buzansky Selsoviet, Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 196 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Astrakhan, 29 km from Krasny Yar. == References == Category:Rural localities in Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Allaysky
